<i>her because I loved her so much.</i>

963
01:24:24,625 --> 01:24:32,958
{\an8}<i>It may be impossible to name all of Momâ€™s good</i>
<i>qualities, but one certainty is I would not have</i>

964
01:24:33,167 --> 01:24:38,375
{\an8}<i>a chance at life or success</i>
<i>if it wasnâ€™t for Mom and Children's Village.</i>

965
01:24:39,000 --> 01:24:50,375
{\an8}<i>I feel that my relationship with</i>
<i>my mother goes beyond mother-daughter love.</i>

966
01:24:50,500 --> 01:24:58,042
{\an8}<i>My mother was a good teacher,</i>
<i>and I think every mother should be.</i>

967
01:25:05,375 --> 01:25:09,792
{\an8}<i>My mother was very upset with me</i>
<i>for walking away from a more stable life.</i>

968
01:25:09,833 --> 01:25:11,833
{\an8}<i>She wouldn't speak with me.</i>

969
01:25:11,875 --> 01:25:19,583
{\an8}<i>When I first opened the school,</i>
<i>she didn't understand. It was such a new concept.</i>

970
01:25:19,625 --> 01:25:25,458
{\an8}<i>She didn't see why I left the public school system,</i>
<i>which was secure and safe</i>

971
01:25:25,708 --> 01:25:32,333
{\an8}<i>in exchange for much harder</i>
<i>living conditions in the jungle.</i>

972
01:25:32,542 --> 01:25:41,417
{\an8}<i>So, after three years I went to visit, and</i>
<i>because I couldn't put my reasons into words</i>

973
01:25:41,542 --> 01:25:48,500
{\an8}<i>I took some of the children with me</i>
<i>and told my mother their stories</i>

974
01:25:48,833 --> 01:25:53,167
{\an8}<i>about their hardships and</i>
<i>my mother understood and supported me.</i>

975
01:25:56,750 --> 01:26:01,625
{\an8}<i>If you are listening think of me.</i>

976
01:26:01,750 --> 01:26:07,750
{\an8}<i>I promise I will be a good child.</i>

977
01:26:12,208 --> 01:26:18,833
{\an8}<i>If there is someone who worries all the time</i>

978
01:26:19,792 --> 01:26:25,792
{\an8}<i>Who gives up her time and energy selflessly.</i>

979
01:26:26,333 --> 01:26:33,375
{\an8}<i>If there is someone who keeps her pain to herself</i>

980
01:26:33,417 --> 01:26:38,333
{\an8}<i>Thinking more about us than herself.</i>

981
01:26:39,708 --> 01:26:43,500
{\an8}<i>If there is someone...</i>

982
01:26:43,542 --> 01:26:51,167
{\an8}<i>Mother's Day is a reminder of the huge</i>
<i>influence a mother has on her children.</i>

983
01:26:51,583 --> 01:26:56,917
{\an8}<i>A mother is both a parent and a teacher</i>

984
01:26:56,958 --> 01:27:01,667
{\an8}<i>someone of great value to a child.</i>

985
01:27:01,708 --> 01:27:04,917
{\an8}<i>No matter how old you are,</i>

986
01:27:04,958 --> 01:27:12,458
{\an8}<i>when you encounter hardship,</i>
<i>you think of your mother.</i>

987
01:27:12,833 --> 01:27:17,750
{\an8}<i>She is the only one who always forgives me.</i>

988
01:27:17,958 --> 01:27:21,708
{\an8}<i>No matter how many faults</i>

989
01:27:21,875 --> 01:27:25,208
{\an8}<i>that make me a naughty child</i>

990
01:27:25,250 --> 01:27:30,250
{\an8}<i>I know her love will never change.</i>

991
01:27:31,792 --> 01:27:35,958
{\an8}<i>I want to thank you</i>

992
01:27:36,583 --> 01:27:37,625
{\an8}<i>What?</i>

993
01:27:38,917 --> 01:27:50,083
{\an8}<i>My mother had cancer and</i>
<i>I spent her last two months with her and</i>

994
01:27:51,083 --> 01:28:00,583
{\an8}<i>my brother informed me her lungs stopped working</i>
<i>and she would pass within two days.</i>

995
01:28:00,750 --> 01:28:07,333
{\an8}<i>I ran back to Children's Village because</i>
<i>I couldn't bear seeing her die in front of me.</i>

996
01:28:07,417 --> 01:28:13,250
{\an8}<i>I asked my older sister to be</i>
<i>the one to stay and ran back here.</i>

997
01:28:13,292 --> 01:28:21,125
{\an8}<i>So, it may seem that I am a bad person for that,</i>
<i>but I really couldn't bear it</i>

998
01:28:21,708 --> 01:28:23,750
{\an8}<i>because I love her so much.</i>

999
01:28:38,417 --> 01:28:40,250
{\an8}<i>What's wrong?</i>

1000
01:28:41,625 --> 01:28:45,750
{\an8}<i>"I want to thank you". Sing it.</i>

1001
01:28:45,917 --> 01:28:52,833
{\an8}<i>I want to thank you for being my mother</i>

1002
01:28:52,875 --> 01:28:59,000
{\an8}<i>giving me love without exception,</i>
<i>a love like no other.</i>

1003
01:28:59,042 --> 01:29:05,792
{\an8}<i>I will always have you throughout my life.</i>

1004
01:29:05,833 --> 01:29:12,125
{\an8}<i>So I have four little words</i>
<i>to say from my heart.</i>

1005
01:29:12,417 --> 01:29:15,375
{\an8}<i>I love you Mom.</i>

1006
01:29:30,458 --> 01:29:39,500
{\an8}<i>My plan is to build the teachers</i>
<i>and students into the school's new leaders</i>

1007
01:29:39,500 --> 01:29:43,250
{\an8}<i>and I hope I can hand the school off to them one day.</i>

1008
01:29:47,583 --> 01:29:52,458
{\an8}<i>I believe that when I'm gone</i>
<i>and someone takes my place here</i>

1009
01:29:52,583 --> 01:29:59,958
{\an8}<i>they may have their personal ideas</i>
<i>and should run the school according to them.</i>

1010
01:30:00,083 --> 01:30:03,750
{\an8}<i>I think change is fine as long as</i>
<i>the goal is the student's happiness.</i>

1011
01:30:03,875 --> 01:30:06,750
{\an8}<i>Maybe they will even implement a new system.</i>

1012
01:30:16,333 --> 01:30:19,792
{\an8}<i>Thailand is a land of mothers.</i>

1013
01:30:20,250 --> 01:30:28,500
{\an8}<i>because in Thai the word "Mother"</i>
<i>is used in the terms for river, the earth,</i>

1014
01:30:28,625 --> 01:30:35,375
{\an8}<i>rice, and so many</i>
<i>other things in nature are called Mother.</i>

1015
01:30:35,500 --> 01:30:42,625
{\an8}<i>The meaning behind that is</i>
<i>mothers give their children love and warmth</i>

1016
01:30:42,667 --> 01:30:47,958
{\an8}<i>and if you come to Thailand</i>
<i>you'll feel that warmth given to you.</i>

1017
01:30:55,958 --> 01:31:02,042
{\an8}<i>If I look back at my life, from</i>
<i>childhood to now, it's been a happy one.</i>

1018
01:31:02,167 --> 01:31:10,792
{\an8}<i>I was happy with my family as a child,</i>
<i>then I married and became a mother.</i>

1019
01:31:10,833 --> 01:31:18,500
{\an8}<i>I am also proud to be the mother of</i>
<i>300 or 400 students at Children's Village.</i>

1020
01:31:18,750 --> 01:31:20,583
{\an8}<i>I have been fortunate...</i>

1021
01:31:20,875 --> 01:31:27,250
{\an8}<i>...to be among people</i>
<i>I love and who love me.</i>

1022
01:31:27,625 --> 01:31:31,833
{\an8}<i>I feel fortunate to have lived my life.</i>




